* [BitcoinX.com Mining Profitability Calculator](http://bitcoinX.com/profit/) - since 2011-04-14
* [TP's Bitcoin Calculator](http://tpbitcalc.appspot.com/) website (useful for pool mining)
* [Mining Break Even Calculator](http://0x10.org/sandbox/bitcalc/) website (also useful for pool mining)
* [Easy BitCoin Mining Calculator](http://bitcoin.web-share.nl/) website (also useful for pool mining)
